questions.quote: Oh Ross, come on! This is not, this is not a marriage!! This is the world's worst hangover! Ross, listen, if you do not get this annulment, I will!
That's impossible! I mean we have had a deal for years! We-we-we shook on it, although believe me she wanted to do a lot more than that.
Y'know, I-I could see how this could happen, y'know you're up there every night, you're naked, touching, kissing.
Well sweetie, we have a surprise for you. We're turning your room into a gym.
I just left you a message! Ross and I were gonna go grab a bite, but now that you're here, maybe we can go have that dinner.
Just you keep it, listen did you, did you tell anyone about us?
Look what I found in the drawer... And you said I'd never wear this...
Well, I'm just saying, I mean why else would he just, y'know, swoop in out of nowhere for no reason.

Oh, come on! He's glad that I came, he doesn't want me to go anywhere, balls flying all over the place!
